@node "History" "History"
@next "Thanks"
@prev "Quasar Settings"
                           @{b}@{u}HISTORY@{ub}@{uu}

Version    Date         Changes
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

- 0.07     ??????       Initial coding and hacking.


V 0.08     23-11-94     Added envelope window.


V 0.09     05-12-94     GUI redesign. Lots of internal changes.


V 0.10     09-12-94     Added names of drum sounds.
                        First version of performance editors.
                        Internal code redesign.


V 0.11     10-12-94     QED now allows to edit the performances.
                        Minor changes in the ARP sources.


V 0.12     11-12-94     Additional work on performance editor.


V 0.13     15-12-94     Fixed drumsets error.
                        Fixed part selection offset error. 
                        Added support for drumset selection.
                        Envelope editor now works in performance mode.


V 0.14     18-12-94     Fixed display error of titlebar (drum editor).
                        QED now supports different performance banks.
                        New "Write to...." button.
                        Load performance map fixed.
                        Fixed: QED crashed when CheckQuasar()
                        failed  (DICE error !).
                        Minor GUI changes. 
                        QED now recognizes performances program changes.


V 0.15     20-12-94     Env display was not updated by incoming
                        level messages.
                        New preferences option: Autowrite for performances.
                        Minor changes in the Preferences code.
                        QED transmitted ARP parameters for
                        performances wrong.
                        ARP part parameter handling fixed.


V 0.16     21-12-94     QED now supports *ALL* performance banks.
                        Major changes in the performance MIDI code.
                        Fixed minor bug in GetPerfPartParameters().
                        Added Panic button.


V 0.17     25-12-94     Support for external parts (GM mode).
                        Added editor for program changes.
                        Fixed bug in LoadMap().
                        Hopefully fixed strange bug: replaced UBYTE params
                        by INT params. 
                        Added Modulation Matrix button in the 
                        GM editor window.


V 0.18     29-12-94     Minor changes in the System window.
                        MIDI stuff is now much safer and is able to
                        handle MIDI deadlocks.
                        Minor internal changes.
                        Reworked "Load/Save all".
                        Fixed ugly Enforcer hits :-)
                        Sound selector window: last sound 
                        wasn't displayed :-(
                        Parameter control was sometimes switched of by QED.
                        Changed LV notifications (no more double clicks).
                        Performance maps are now cached.
                        First version of documentation in Amigaguide format.



V 0.19     15-01-95     Fixed bug in init().    
                        Fixed bug in LoadAllPerformances().
                        Added test options for GM sounds.
                        Rearranged performance editor sources.
                        Changed performance map caching


V 0.20     19-01-95     New QED icon by Christian 'Kochtopf' Scholz.
                        Minor changes in Iconify() code.
                        Updated installer script.
                        Added NofileWarning(). 
                        Changed outfit of QED settings window.
                        Fixed links in Amigaguide file.
                        Serial port is freed while QED is iconified.
                        All Menu title were named "Unnamed" (MUIB bug)
                        (used MUIA_MenuitemObject instead MUIA_MenuObject).
                        get()ing MUIA_Window_Open seems to be corrupt in 
                        MUI 2.3.
                        Reworked online help code (HELP key disabled !!!!) -
                        use menu item "Help" instead.
                        Fixed bug in realtime editing (Quasar -> QED).
                        Reworked OverwriteRequest().
                        Added some Delay()s in GetPerfMapNames() - hopefully
                        no more crashes on non-QED-compatible Amigas :-))))


V 0.21   09-02-95       Updated Guide file.
                        Minor internal changes in sources.
                        Wrong sound patterns (soundlist) caused to crash QED.
                        New feature planned: performance library.  
                        Fixed bug in SED script (Dice does not recognize 
                        double declared structure members :-(((( )


V 0.22   26-02-95       New: Performance Library
                        "Copy" in Performance mode didn't work proberly.
                        Some internal structs are now allocated dynamicly,
                        this saves about 250 KB memory while runing QED.
                        Updated Installer script.
                        Minor GUI changes.
                        QED settings were not updated correctly.
                        Fixed: PerfLib/Remove() error.
                        New: QED settings/Library path.


V 0.98   26-04-95       Bumped up revision because QED is in the final
                        release state.



 Known bugs: 
 ----------- 
 - none :-)


 To do: 
 ------ 
 - better input handling within the envelope editor 
 - better system performance
@endnode

